or maybe he isn't.

363
00:19:33,423 --> 00:19:35,884
And maybe he killed
Jason Blossom, and...

364
00:19:40,556 --> 00:19:41,431
Oh, sorry.

365
00:19:43,267 --> 00:19:45,060
